      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I need help writing a rejection email. We had a candidate, Marcus, who made it all the way to the final interview for our Senior Dev role here in Austin. He's really talented and had great technical skills, but we decided to go with someone who had a bit more experience with our specific cloud architecture. I want the email to be professional and kind because he was a great guy, but we need to be firm that the decision is final. Can you draft something?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
