      "content": "Here's a draft rejection email:\n\nDear Marcus,\n\nWe wanted to personally reach out and express our sincere appreciation for the time and effort you invested in our Senior Developer role at [Company Name]. Your technical skills and experience are truly impressive, and we were particularly pleased with your insights during our final interview. Although we ultimately decided to move forward with another candidate whose background aligned more closely with our specific cloud architecture needs, please know that this decision was in no way a reflection on your abilities or potential as a developer. We wish you the very best in your ongoing search and gratitude for considering [Company Name].\n\nBest regards, [Your Name]",
